headline: Caesars to transform Harveys Lake Tahoe into Caesars Republic Lake Tahoe
summary: Caesars (CZR) Entertainment announced its plans to transform Harveys Lake Tahoe into Caesars Republic Lake Tahoe Hotel & Casino this summer. The $160M renovation will include state-of-the-art upgrades, luxurious accommodations and elevated dining and gaming options while immersing guests in a new, contemporary resort designed to embrace the look and feel of Lake Tahoe.
